_:Nbc71962fe1c74f67ab32849d5ff91186 <http://schema.org/description> "The Parades Commission for Northern Ireland (PCNI) is independent of government. It has the power to place restrictions on public processions and related protest meetings. PCNI is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Northern Ireland Office ." .
